:

1. *Volje* su moćne snage u našim životima. (Wills are powerful forces in our lives.)
2. Želim da promenim svet, ali nemam dovoljno *volje*. (I want to change the world, but I don't have enough will.)
3. Oni su uvek imali dovoljno *volje* da naprave promene. (They always had enough will to make changes.)
4. *Volja* je bila važna kako bi ostvarili naš cilj. (Will was important in order to achieve our goal.)
5. Mladi ljudi često osećaju potrebu da se suprotstave *volji* autoriteta. (Young people often feel the need to oppose the will of authority.)